twentytwo please don't misunderstand me. I - and I'm sure loads of other lurkers - really do appreciate you posting these, and I want to see the videos she posts - but honestly it's turned from simping for the unobtainable thot to watching a dumpsterfire as it unfolds. The only good thing to come out of 2020 was belle posting tits, but now it's her main focus and the quality and creativity in her photo sets has really plummeted. These tapes show total amateur productions, but it's not quaint like amateur porn, it's sad and cringy like amateur film making. Belle will release a shitty clip for way too much money tomorrow, and I think she'll dwindle into memory from there. She'll be laughing to the fucking bank - but the belle delphine porn project will be dead. She'll have lost her fanbase. The magic is really truly dead, but we've been shown a masterclass in business savvy. These are my autistic two cents.
